==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: hen-of-the-woods
<hw>hen-of-the-woods</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A large grayish-brown
edible fungus (<spn>Polyporus frondosus</spn>) forming a mass of
overlapping caps at the base of trees that somewhat resembles a
hen.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> hen of the woods, <spn>Polyporus
frondosus</spn>.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Henrietta cloth</ent>⟦br⟧
